name: super free fall
description:
A Meditations game - Monday October 14

In october 14th of 2012 Felix Baumgartner made th highest sky dive ever and while this was a great record moment, there were some dangerous moments, he probably felt dizzy and spinned out of controle in the air, but he got the control back and could land safely, this is was a nice, but also a tense moment, we'd love that this days was remembered giving players tension to keep stable while diving.
